page_title: Plan to manage costs for Azure OpenAI Service
page_description: Learn how to plan for and manage costs for Azure OpenAI by using cost analysis in the Azure portal.
chunk_content: PrerequisitesCost analysis in Cost Management supports most Azure account types, but not all of them. To view the full list of supported account types, see Understand Cost Management data. To view cost data, you need at least read access for an Azure account. For information about assigning access to Azure Cost Management data, see Assign access to data.
